,"msg":"我都好奇怪而家下下都吹呢套<br />\n明明出果陣都唔算好好評<br />\n我果陣有斷斷續續睇<br />\n覺得係完全係劣版IS<br />\n到今日IS冇人提反而套差幾皮既俾人吹神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f84eac22b64cac240729e50149b12babbca1e41c","tid":614603,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2eae20e4449554db534d1a3ba15be256238fd07d","tid":614603,"uid":32221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"31882cec7928da940d21f11001284fa794047077","tid":614603,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T06:09:04.000Z","msg":"去到一半拖到仆街+垃圾結局<br />\n根本就唔係咩神作"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T16:25:05.000Z","msg":"我都好奇怪而家下下都吹呢套<br />\n明明出果陣都唔算好好評<br />\n我果陣有斷斷續續睇<br />\n覺得係完全係劣版IS<br />\n到今日IS冇人提反而套差幾皮既俾人吹神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T02:13:28.000Z","msg":"嗰陣連載到一半已經拖撚到仆街<br />\n好似五月色誘男角唔上釣之類嘅後宮劇情都loop咗好多次畀人話鳩佢悶<br />\n<br />\n再之後加咗個女角(補習社怕羞嗰個)，冇乜點講過就去咗ending<br />\n明明就係爛爛哋唔多完整，仲要整個首尾不一嘅ending<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n河下啲作品其實真係冇乜話邊本特別好睇<br />\n根本佢成功某程上係因為佢嘅畫功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好睇我覺得係給我一吻(親親小魔女), 呢套係草莓對上一套連載嚟<br />\n勝在夠短冇點拖，節奏快，故事首尾都完整<br />\n雖然可能都係被腰斬，但起碼我覺得佢完整過草莓先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw, 連登仔吹捧嘅火影(naruto)咪又係咁<br />\n明明去到第二部之後都畀人屌到仆街<br />\n而家啲人又話咩佩恩自來也好好睇，好感動<br />\n明明當年畀人屌到仆街話佢爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9cf4dea0d32d6f970ca74e5790abfb9e27a0b12","tid":614603,"uid":2707,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T02:17:16.000Z","msg":"btw, 冇記錯i's劇情比較寫實，冇咁多固定套路(鹹濕嘢&gt;最後冇事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n雖然呢本我覺佢去到最尾都悶悶哋，又有啲誇張劇情咁<br />\n唔太算上乘之作，又係賣畫功成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ndna2應該仲好睇啲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7505b8f6b56af0e43f0458a2eaa924977dcccd8d","tid":614603,"uid":39177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T02:23:09.000Z","msg":"東城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n北大路就明顯陪跑<br />\n<br />\n呢套野性格描寫好寫實"},{"pid":"cb152c469d54cdeb225ae489fcdfc8bbe8d07c98","tid":614603,"uid":38172,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T02:31:07.000Z","msg":"支持主角同東城<br />\n<br />\n但俾我揀, 我揀北大路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d051be202a39e507d4fd029c3c75fee6e3cba5","tid":614603,"uid":53732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T02:35:01.000Z","msg":"I's 正過草莓"},{"pid":"8c61859de03099c4741dad4a0922b720687094c3","tid":614603,"uid":148673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:12:32.000Z","msg":"北大路<br />\n專一義無反顧<br />\n平時又啱傾又好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁好嘅女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d028f7b89ba32a936cdc3a1d83bb3963f754abe","tid":614603,"uid":105364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:40:40.000Z","msg":"以前就覺得最想要東,有共同興趣,又怕怕羞羞,好可愛<br />\n大個睇多次, 反而覺得北最好, 好相處又直接爽快"},{"pid":"4e5498fddc1c69b4014f0c5d135b1781a3108b57","tid":614603,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:25:19.000Z","msg":"東軍路過！"},{"pid":"b8606fa5d12b3fad85189b230b4644bfff218de3","tid":614603,"uid":169468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:30:40.000Z","msg":"中學睇完結果睇到心噏到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n特登買咗一套收藏<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"